(2148, 1, '2020-04-28 10:41:27', '2020-04-28 10:41:27', 'Join us in democratizing access to energy\r\n\r\nOver 1.2 billion, one in five people in the world, do not have access to electricity\r\n\r\nEven in areas connected to the grid electricity is often unreliable. Without access to affordable electricity, most families in rural areas must derive energy from generators or lamp oil (kerosene) which is hazardous, unhealthy and cost up to 37% of household income.\r\n\r\nThe pay-as-you-go solar energy system for families in the developing world\r\n\r\nM-PAYG is a provider of high-quality prepaid solar energy systems for the developing world. Our systems allow off-grid low-income households and businesses to access solar energy through small-scale mobile repayments. To use the system you unlock it through weekly or monthly mobile repayments.', 'M-PAYG', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'm-payg-product', '', '', '2020-05-06 01:27:50', '2020-05-06 01:27:50', '', 0, 'http://mpaygtech.local:81/?post_type=product&#038;p=2148', 0, 'product', '', 0),
